Subject: Help With Building Reports
Description:
Hi,

I have a user who is asking for a few reports that Im having trouble figuring out and am hoping you can help with.

1) I need a report that will pull from Azure all user names that begin with AZ
2) A list of Groups from Active Directory that have Members beginning with VO DA or PO contained within the group. 
3) A list of users that are not a member of any group policies.
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issue]
Customer was looking for a 3 custom reports:
1. All Azure usernames beginning with "AZ"
2. AD Groups that have members beginning with V0, DA, or P0
3. Users not affected by group policy

[Resolution]
1. Built a SQLviewcreation analysis under the EntraID2. UsersAAD_List of AZ Users job that will filter the SA_AzureADInventory_UsersView to DisplayNames that begin with AZ
2. Built a SQLviewcreation analysis under the Active DirectoryALI.PRI1.GroupsAD_GroupsWithPrivMembers job that will filter the SA_ADInventory_GroupMembersView to SAMAccountNames that begin with V0, DA, and P0
3. I offered to reach out to proserv or open a fr because this is not something available oob but they never responded.
